{"tid":657434,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一個post，就睇到你條傻鳩個人品行係點","createTime":"2018-05-08T06:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T10:01:11.000Z","uid":18679,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1744d60443be5ce61d70c66b18b88ef391208701","tid":657434,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"條傻9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n禮儀既本意就係表示尊重別人 尊重自己<br />\n睇條傻9都知佢現實只係識餐桌禮儀<br />\n一講野肯定粗粗魯魯 得罪人多稱呼人少既老粗黎<br />\n「捨本逐末」就係攞黎笑9呢d學完餐桌禮儀之後走去屌9人無禮儀既傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學禮而反禮就係佢呢個人思考既最大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「夫禮者，所以定親疏，決嫌疑，別同異，明是非也。」（禮不單指禮儀）<br />\n是是非非都未搞清楚 返屋企讀多d禮儀書先上網啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw去日本旅行記得唔好屌人食拉麵食到雪雪聲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申個人唔識咩禮儀 但都唔會屌人無家教"},{"pid":"b645f6370e4f816debb163811f082778a6fe0c77","tid":657434,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開post嗰位話食緊嗰陣望下枱面啲送都唔得<br />\n幾惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當其他同枱食飯嘅人係狗"},{"pid":"24f2674a1a5c23d13d2494a44264efe6f8b52565","tid":657434,"uid":174488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4f00877eef5d5d606e6f81a384dc0964d8a1148","tid":657434,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:13:38.000Z","msg